21
00:02:24,599 --> 00:02:25,120
There's enough for everyone

22
00:02:25,199 --> 00:02:25,960
This is wonderful

23
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,360
You ruin your own future

24
00:02:55,719 --> 00:02:56,639
Do you truly not regret it?

25
00:03:06,439 --> 00:03:07,240
In one's lifetime

26
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:10,120
You must do a few things
that make you proud

27
00:03:10,879 --> 00:03:12,120
Big, passionate things

28
00:03:12,919 --> 00:03:14,000
The nation is its people

29
