34
00:03:26,599 --> 00:03:27,479
Lying on a rocking chair

35
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,280
Looking back on my life

36
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:33,039
Only then will it all be worth it

37
00:03:33,919 --> 00:03:34,759
Truly meaningful

38
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,960
Be an official like Shi Feifan

39
