44
00:03:51,759 --> 00:03:52,280
Alright then

45
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:53,280
When we reach the capital

46
00:03:53,759 --> 00:03:55,360
I'll have a good drink with you

47
00:03:56,719 --> 00:03:57,199
Alright

48
00:04:00,719 --> 00:04:01,680
It's finally done

49
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:03,400
The three-day deadline is here

50
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:05,000
Lord Shi, it's time to go

51
00:04:11,759 --> 00:04:13,159
Even if I agree to go back with you

52
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:16,199
I might not make it back alive

53
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:17,439
It's not that I don't trust you

54
00:04:18,199 --> 00:04:19,600
But Nan Batian kills without warning

55
00:04:20,439 --> 00:04:22,759
The journey back may be dangerous

56
00:04:27,639 --> 00:04:28,480
Don't worry, Lord Shi

57
00:04:28,879 --> 00:04:30,959
I'll risk my life to protect yours

58
00:05:06,759 --> 00:05:07,680
Shi Feifan

59
00:05:08,399 --> 00:05:09,839
Do you have anything else to say?

60
00:05:11,079 --> 00:05:13,879
