completed the resettlement

61
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:15,560
Today I return to report in the capital

62
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:18,040
Resettlement is complete

63
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:20,680
You disregard the law

64
00:05:20,879 --> 00:05:22,199
You killed a prince

65
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,600
Is this your way of resettling?

66
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:30,240
Extraordinary times call for
extraordinary actions

67
00:05:30,399 --> 00:05:32,160
If I hadn't killed Liang Qing
or divided the land

68
00:05:32,399 --> 00:05:34,079
